				  We are launching our <a style="color:#75ACED; text-decoration:none;" href="https://www.ably.io/dsx">Data Stream Exchange</a> platform which lets you stream your data seamlessly to other businesses. <a style="color:#75ACED; text-decoration:none;" href="mailto:support@ably.io">Get in touch for early access</a>.
				</mj-text>
			</mj-column>
		</mj-section>
